---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/layout/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
import TrustStrip from '../components/ui/TrustStrip.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Free Promise — Why Liaison.legal Is Free for Parents, Forever"
  description="Liaison.legal is free for parents with no payment screen anywhere in the app. Here's exactly what's free, why, and how we keep the lights on."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gray-100 py-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-navy mb-6">
          Free for parents. Forever. And we mean it structurally.
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Plenty of apps say "free." We built ours so that a parent literally cannot be charged —
          there is no parent payment screen anywhere in Liaison.legal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Answer-first -->
    <section class="bg-white py-10 px-6 border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-body text-base text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Liaison.legal is free for parents, permanently and unconditionally. There is no parent
          payment rail in the product, no premium parent tier, and no credit card required to use
          any parent feature. You can document your co-parenting communication for as long as you
          like — whether or not you ever hire an attorney. Liaison.legal earns revenue from law
          firms, not from parents.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sections -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-16">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy mb-4">
            What "free" actually covers
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-base text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Everything a parent uses: secure messaging, the tamper-evident ledger, read and open
            receipts, complete searchable history, document storage, and the verified record itself.
            All of it. No usage caps designed to push you into paying.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy mb-4">
            Why we can promise this
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-base text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Documenting your communication should never depend on what you can afford — it's the
            part that protects you. So parents don't pay. Law firms do, when they're pulled into
            an active matter and use the record as part of their work. The parent who's simply
            keeping an honest record is never the customer.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-gray-400 italic">
            "Free for parents" means documentation is free. It does not mean litigation is free —
            courts, attorneys, and filings have their own costs, set by them, not by us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy mb-4">
            No ads. No selling your data. Not ever.
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-base text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Liaison.legal does not run ads, does not sell or share your data with advertisers,
            and does not build a profile of you to monetize. In a record meant for court, that
            isn't just a privacy preference — a monetized record invites attacks on its neutrality.
            Neutrality is the whole point.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-navy py-16 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
        <a
          href="https://app.liaison.legal/signup"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-azure text-white font-body font-semibold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200 mb-6"
        >
          Start Free Account →
        </a>
        <div class="text-white/70"><TrustStrip /></div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
